data.description: This lovely well-maintained 4 Bedroom 2 1/2 Bath plus Den home on a conservation lot is located in the desirable community of Concord Station won't last long!  Extra Bonus loft can be used for playroom, office, etc.  Community boasts resort-like amenities -- including a new splashpad, playground, 5,000 ft. clubhouse, fitness center, community pool and park.  Close to shopping, restaurants and easy access to all major highways.  REFRIGERATOR DOES NOT CONVEY.  WASHER/DRYER CONVEYS WITH FULL PRICE OFFER.
